            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I don't think the assumption here is correct: `inherits` is explicitly for _other_ languages; if you want to \"inherit\" from other queries for the _same_ language, you need to use `extends` (you can combine both for your case). This is explicitly [documented](https://neovim.io/doc/user/treesitter.html#treesitter-query-modeline).\n\nPlease test if adding `; extends` to your custom query works.",
