            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Tested only using `; inherits: custom`. The issue persist:\n\n- `custom` injections work\n- base `lua` injections do not work\n\n---\n\n> This is explicitly [documented](https://neovim.io/doc/user/treesitter.html#treesitter-query-modeline).\n\nYes, I know the differences between `inherits` and `extends`. I used `inherits` because that is what I readed in [the example code](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/9fa7c0a04638ee3d5fefbdcec347b1c07a5ce9ce/runtime/doc/treesitter.txt#L1540-L1545).\n\n---\n\n> Please test if adding `; extends` to your custom query works.\n\nYes, this works. I already [used it](https://github.com/Hdoc1509/vim-map-side.nvim/commit/8b87bdc51b5043b61582dc156dfdc81b3c453864).",
